title: The Books of Earthsea Illustrated Ed. by Ursula K. Le Guin(epub)
description:
The Books of Earthsea: The Complete Illustrated Edition by Ursula K. Le Guin

Requirements: .ePUB, .MOBI/.AZW3 reader

Overview: Celebrating the 50th anniversary of the timeless and beloved A Wizard of Earthsea - '...reads like the retelling of a tale first told centuries ago' (David Mitchell) - comes this complete omnibus edition of the entire Earthsea chronicles, including over fifty illustrations illuminating Le Guin's vision of her classic saga.

Genre: Fiction > Sci-Fi/Fantasy
